Make a GUI, which has the following necessities:
A menu, with an option to choose each cousin. And sub-menus to make further choices. 



It should take you through the complex process that occurs when you run a simple program. 

It will be disclaimed in advance that these things are NOT fully operational. Our scope is limited to minimum lines of code, as we wanted to show you 
in quick and easy ways how these steps take place. The actual compilers are much more in-depth and work across entire KLOCs. 


